  "texts": [
    "In recent years, transformers 41 have started to perform well in high-dimensional settings such as audio 42, 43.",
    "This is particularly the case when models are first trained in a self-supervised manner on unlabelled audio data.",
    "We adopt the SSAST 44, which is on a par with the current state of the art for audio event classification.",
    "Raw audio is first resampled to 16 kHz and normalized before being transformed into Mel filter banks.",
    "Strided convolutional neural layers are used to project the Mel filter bank to a series of patch level representations."
  ],
